To make the salad, place the onion rings and chilli into a large bowl.Drizzle the olive oil over and add the lime juice and mangetout. Toss together.To make the dressing, whisk the mustard, wine, olive oil, chilli flakes and balsamic vinegar in a jug or bowl until combined.Transfer the salad to a serving plate or bowl. Drizzle the dressing over to serve.